title: Businessweek Talks- Kayak CEO Steve Hafner
itunes:title: Businessweek Talks- Kayak CEO Steve Hafner
description:
Steve Hafner, CEO at Kayak, says consumers are at least beginning to think about flying again and restaurants are selling every table they can. He speaks with Bloomberg Businessweek anchors Carol Massar and Jason Kelly in the latest edition of Businessweek Talks.

Producer: Doni Holloway.
